安迪·泰勒表示，他退出杜兰·杜兰的原因是“创意，而不是个人” https://www.nme.com/news/music/andy-taylor-says-the-reason-he-quit-duran-duran-was-creative-not-personal-3489429?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=andy-泰勒说他退出杜兰杜兰的原因是创意而非个人Hollie GeraghtySun, 27 Aug 2023 17:11:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3489429 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran) 的约翰·泰勒 (左) 和安迪·泰勒" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这不是为了按我自己的方式行事”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andy-taylor-says-the-reason-he-quit-duran-duran-was-creative-not-personal-3489429">安迪·泰勒 (Andy Taylor) 表示，他退出杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran) 的原因是“创意，而非个人”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran) 的约翰·泰勒 (左) 和安迪·泰勒" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/andy-taylor-duran-duran-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duran-duran">杜兰·杜兰乐队</a>的安迪·泰勒透露，他退出乐队的原因是“创作”原因，“并非个人原因”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/duran-duran-interview-2023-simon-le-bon-john-taylor-glastonbury-wet-leg-3432534">杜兰·杜兰（Duran Duran）：“我们很乐意举办格拉斯顿伯里音乐节——我们只需要合适的位置”</a></strong></li></ul><p>泰勒在 1980 年至 2006 年间断断续续地与杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran) 一起演奏， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-to-reunite-with-former-guitarist-for-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-induction-3221589">去年他们</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-duran-duran-dolly-parton-and-lionel-richie-to-be-inducted-into-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-3218338">入选摇滚名人堂</a>时，泰勒原定与他们重聚，但他在治疗第四期转移性前列腺癌时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-durans-andy-taylor-misses-hall-of-fame-ceremony-due-to-cancer-treatment-3343601">遇到了</a>挫折。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-durans-andy-taylor-misses-hall-of-fame-ceremony-due-to-cancer-treatment-3343601">他就错过了这个机会</a>。</p><p>这位 62 岁的音乐家在经历了数十年的不和传闻后，现在公开了他退出新浪潮乐队的原因，并表示这是“创造性的，而不是个人的”。</p><p>在<em>经典流行</em>杂志（通过<em><a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/163130/Duran-Duran-s-Andy-Taylor-had-a-creative-not-personal-rift-with-his-bandmates" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MusicNews</a></em> ）的新采访中，这位吉他手表示，乐队为 2007 年专辑《<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-23-1292154">红地毯大屠杀</a>》引入了更广泛的圈子，这让他“烦恼”，该专辑主要由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timbaland">Timbaland</a>制作。</p><p> “我无法制作 Timbaland 专辑，因为它没有打动我，”他说。 “我对其他人说，‘我们为什么需要这个？’</p><p> “那个乐队里有很多才华横溢的人，我从来没有觉得有必要带其他人来和杜兰一起创作。这让我很烦恼。”他继续说道：“这并不是为了按我自己的方式行事。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Duran Duran 谈新音乐《Wet Leg》和他们的格拉斯顿伯里梦想 |谈话中" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-B-IVaTCP3k?start=139&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他补充说，他无法把乐队放在第一位，并分享道：“普遍的感觉是，‘你应该和我们一起来这里’，但我做不到。我不知道是什么让我无法做到这一点。</p><p> “感觉就像有人把电梯门关在我身上，我无法通过。必须有一种平衡，但我感觉不到。我的感觉和我在[1986 年专辑]《Notorious》离开时的感觉一样：“我会再次怀念这一切。”</p><p>早在三月份，杜兰·杜兰<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-will-reportedly-reunite-with-andy-taylor-on-upcoming-album-3417078">就表示他们“正在制作一张专辑，将于年底发行”</a> ，泰勒将在其中弹吉他。</p><p>本周，他们宣布将于 8 月 30 日推出新单曲“Danse Macabre”。</p><p>本月早些时候，泰勒表示，他正在服用的一种治疗癌症的药物<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-andy-taylor-nuclear-cancer-drug-given-him-five-more-years-3481770">已将他的生命延长了五年</a>，他于 2018 年被诊断出患有这种癌症。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andy-taylor-says-the-reason-he-quit-duran-duran-was-creative-not-personal-3489429">安迪·泰勒 (Andy Taylor) 表示，他退出杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran) 的原因是“创意，而非个人”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇透露，她接受了“紧急手术”，“救了我的命” https://www.nme.com/news/music/florence-welch-reveals-that-she-has-had-emergency-surgery-that-saved-my-life-3489419?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=florence-韦尔奇透露她接受了紧急手术挽救了我的生命Will RichardsSun, 27 Aug 2023 16:32:24 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3489419 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《佛罗伦萨与机器》的弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本周不得不取消两场演出的弗洛伦斯表示，这次手术与之前的足部问题无关</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/florence-welch-reveals-that-she-has-had-emergency-surgery-that-saved-my-life-3489419">弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇 (Florence Welch) 的帖子透露，她接受了“紧急手术”，“救了我的命”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《佛罗伦萨与机器》的弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_florenceandthemachine_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-and-the-machine">Florence + The Machine</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-welch">Florence Welch</a>透露，她接受了“紧急手术”，“挽救了我的生命”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/florence-the-machine-dance-fever-3223402">Florence + The Machine – 《舞蹈狂热》评论：歌手重生的胜利之声</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队不得不“根据医疗建议”取消了最近在苏黎世露天音乐节和塞纳河音乐节上的两场演出，韦尔奇现在在 Instagram 上向歌迷解释了原因。</p><p> “我很抱歉，我不得不取消最后几场演出，”她写道，并解释说，这<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/florence-the-machine-postpone-rest-of-uk-tour-due-to-broken-foot-my-heart-is-aching-3352125">与导致年初英国巡演推迟的脚部骨折</a>无关。</p><p> “我的脚很好，我不得不接受紧急手术，因为我感觉还不够强壮，无法进入，但这救了我的命。”</p><p> Welch went on to add that she will go ahead with the final two shows of the band&#39;s world tour behind 2022 album <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/florence-the-machine-dance-fever-3223402">&#39;Dance Fever&#39;</a> in Lisbon and Malaga next week (September 1-2).</p><p> “Suffice to say I wish the songs were less accurate in their predictions,” she added. “But creativity is a way of coping, mythology is way of making sense. And the dark fairytale of &#39;Dance Fever&#39;, with all its strange prophecies, will provide me with much needed strength and catharsis right now.” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cwc8oMEtwUD/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-